(1, 7, 'About us', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">We have a simple dream. A simple dream to simplify the business of thousands. To connect Business and create opportunity for millions. But a dream like this never comes easy. Connecting the business and Making the business avenue easy and smooth, takes hard work. It means taking the longest route. And the road less travelled. Not settling for the first idea. In fact, not settling at all.</span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.2;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Many say, we complicate our lives just to simplify it for others. That\'s why we are what we are. </span><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">success of your partner’s business is the most important thing to us. We will provide you with the right tools at the right time to scale your business and take it to the next level.</span></p><p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-e8ec378d-7fff-5f4b-7aac-7d521888df31\"></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.295;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:8pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">we offer practical services since we have the know how to guarantee seamless service to our partner. no matter which country you are planning to expand your business, we are here to serve you!</span></p>', 1, 1, 1, NULL, '2022-09-14 05:04:11', '2022-09-14 05:04:11'),
(2, 7, 'Mission', '<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-8638be8e-7fff-00dd-725e-4ffff90efdc2\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Efficiently facilitate contact with professionals in the area of ​​business in Asia, middle east, Europe, north&nbsp; America, South America. Business relation with this regions are managed and maintained with responsibility and high levels of integrity to meet the current and future needs of our partners,achieving the goals proposed by the parties leading to long-term success. Establish all the margins of confidentiality and loyalty to the members of the company as well as to our clients, all working in a dynamic work environment with strengthening in the knowledge of different industrial business areas that challenged the fulfillment of challenges within Plug Limited and with the clients. Demonstrate an environment of harmonious professionals willing to meet each expectation in the best way.</span></span><br></p>', 1, 1, 1, NULL, '2022-09-14 05:04:37', '2022-09-14 05:04:37'),
(3, 7, 'vision', '<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-c1af01cc-7fff-6805-aea1-edbf47858514\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">To be recognized globally as a company capable of providing the best strategies and contacts in the business and import area with comprehensive professionals who provide confidence to our individual and business clients, in addition to providing a work environment that offers comprehensive growth, which Together they will immediately lead to Plug Limited\'s recognition in the industry.</span></span><br></p>', 1, 1, 1, NULL, '2022-09-14 05:05:04', '2022-09-14 05:05:04'),
(4, 9, 'first part', '<h2 data-start=\"285\" data-end=\"308\">Terms &amp; Conditions</h2><p data-start=\"309\" data-end=\"336\"><strong data-start=\"309\" data-end=\"336\">Insight Quality Control</strong></p><p data-start=\"338\" data-end=\"514\">These Terms &amp; Conditions (“Terms”) govern all business activities, products, and services provided by <strong data-start=\"440\" data-end=\"467\">Insight Quality Control</strong> (“the Company”) to its clients (“the Client”).</p><hr data-start=\"516\" data-end=\"519\"><h3 data-start=\"521\" data-end=\"547\">1. Scope of Business</h3><p data-start=\"548\" data-end=\"830\">Insight Quality Control is engaged in the manufacturing, sourcing, quality control, inspection, and supply of garments accessories and apparel products. All services and products shall be provided in accordance with mutually agreed specifications, samples, and written instructions.</p><hr data-start=\"832\" data-end=\"835\"><h3 data-start=\"837\" data-end=\"867\">2. Orders &amp; Confirmation</h3><ul data-start=\"868\" data-end=\"1205\">\r\n<li data-start=\"868\" data-end=\"975\">\r\n<p data-start=\"870\" data-end=\"975\">All orders must be confirmed in writing through email, work order, purchase order, or formal agreement.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"976\" data-end=\"1099\">\r\n<p data-start=\"978\" data-end=\"1099\">Production shall commence only after final approval of samples, designs, specifications, and receipt of agreed payment.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1100\" data-end=\"1205\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1102\" data-end=\"1205\">Any modification requested after approval may result in additional cost and revised delivery timelines.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><hr data-start=\"1207\" data-end=\"1210\"><h3 data-start=\"1212\" data-end=\"1244\">3. Pricing &amp; Payment Terms</h3><ul data-start=\"1245\" data-end=\"1542\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1245\" data-end=\"1346\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1247\" data-end=\"1346\">All prices are quoted in Bangladeshi Taka (BDT) or other agreed currency unless stated otherwise.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1347\" data-end=\"1440\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1349\" data-end=\"1440\">Payment terms (advance, partial, or full payment) shall be strictly as agreed in writing.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1441\" data-end=\"1542\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1443\" data-end=\"1542\">The Company reserves the right to suspend production or delivery in case of delayed or non-payment.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><hr data-start=\"1544\" data-end=\"1547\"><h3 data-start=\"1549\" data-end=\"1578\">4. Delivery &amp; Lead Time</h3><ul data-start=\"1579\" data-end=\"1905\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1579\" data-end=\"1693\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1581\" data-end=\"1693\">Delivery timelines are estimates and depend on timely approval, material availability, and payment compliance.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1694\" data-end=\"1905\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1696\" data-end=\"1905\">The Company shall not be liable for delays caused by force majeure events including but not limited to natural disasters, labor unrest, political instability, transportation disruptions, or government actions.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><hr data-start=\"1907\" data-end=\"1910\"><h3 data-start=\"1912\" data-end=\"1951\">5. Quality Assurance &amp; Inspection</h3><ul data-start=\"1952\" data-end=\"2221\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1952\" data-end=\"2042\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1954\" data-end=\"2042\">Products shall be manufactured in accordance with approved samples and specifications.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2043\" data-end=\"2116\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2045\" data-end=\"2116\">Third-party inspections must be communicated and approved in advance.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2117\" data-end=\"2221\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2119\" data-end=\"2221\">Any quality-related claims must be submitted in writing within <strong data-start=\"2182\" data-end=\"2208\">7 (seven) working days</strong> of delivery.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><hr data-start=\"2223\" data-end=\"2226\"><h3 data-start=\"2228\" data-end=\"2266\">6. Returns, Claims &amp; Adjustments</h3><ul data-start=\"2267\" data-end=\"2543\">\r\n<li data-start=\"2267\" data-end=\"2408\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2269\" data-end=\"2408\">In case of verified non-conformity with approved samples, the Company may, at its discretion, repair, replace, or adjust the claim value.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2409\" data-end=\"2543\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2411\" data-end=\"2543\">No returns or claims shall be accepted for damages arising from improper handling, storage, usage, or transportation after delivery.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><hr data-start=\"2545\" data-end=\"2548\"><h3 data-start=\"2550\" data-end=\"2587\">7. Intellectual Property Rights</h3><ul data-start=\"2588\" data-end=\"2845\">\r\n<li data-start=\"2588\" data-end=\"2705\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2590\" data-end=\"2705\">All designs, trademarks, logos, and branding provided by the Client remain the sole responsibility of the Client.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"2706\" data-end=\"2845\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2708\" data-end=\"2845\">The Company shall not be liable for any intellectual property infringement claims arising from Client-supplied materials or instructions.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><hr data-start=\"2847\" data-end=\"2850\"><h3 data-start=\"2852\" data-end=\"2876\">8. Confidentiality</h3><p data-start=\"2877\" data-end=\"3077\">Both parties agree to maintain strict confidentiality of all commercial, technical, pricing, and design information exchanged during the course of business, except where disclosure is required by law.</p><hr data-start=\"3079\" data-end=\"3082\"><h3 data-start=\"3084\" data-end=\"3116\">9. Limitation of Liability</h3><ul data-start=\"3117\" data-end=\"3314\">\r\n<li data-start=\"3117\" data-end=\"3208\">\r\n<p data-start=\"3119\" data-end=\"3208\">The Company shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"3209\" data-end=\"3314\">\r\n<p data-start=\"3211\" data-end=\"3314\">The maximum liability of the Company shall be limited to the total invoice value of the relevant order.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul><hr data-start=\"3316\" data-end=\"3319\"><h3 data-start=\"3321\" data-end=\"3359\">10. Governing Law &amp; Jurisdiction</h3><p data-start=\"3360\" data-end=\"3543\">These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of <strong data-start=\"3438\" data-end=\"3452\">Bangladesh</strong>, and any disputes shall fall under the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Bangladesh.</p><hr data-start=\"3545\" data-end=\"3548\"><h3 data-start=\"3550\" data-end=\"3570\">11. Amendments</h3><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p data-start=\"3571\" data-end=\"3759\">Insight Quality Control reserves the right to amend or update these Terms &amp; Conditions at any time without prior notice. Updated terms shall be effective upon publication or communication.</p>', 1, 1, 1, NULL, '2026-01-12 23:19:52', '2026-01-12 23:19:52');

